ActEmployment Insurance Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Employment Insurance Regulations
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE (EI) REGULATIONS to remove the requirement for the annual renewal of employer wage-loss plans. The amendments will contribute to efficiency in administering the Premium Reduction Program (PRP) , as well as complementing efforts to streamline and automate administrative processes.
